This plugin runs a self-hosted Python service and depends on third-party
open-source software fetched and run by the consumer — no source code
from those components is bundled in this repository:

  * FastAPI — Sebastián Ramírez et al.
    https://github.com/fastapi/fastapi  (MIT)

  * SQLite — public domain
    https://www.sqlite.org/

  * uvicorn — Encode OSS Ltd.
    https://github.com/encode/uvicorn  (BSD-3-Clause)

  * Model Context Protocol Python SDK — Anthropic
    https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/python-sdk  (MIT)

  * aiosqlite — omnilib
    https://github.com/omnilib/aiosqlite  (MIT)

  * Jinja2 — Pallets Project
    https://github.com/pallets/jinja  (BSD-3-Clause)

  * pydantic-settings — Pydantic team
    https://github.com/pydantic/pydantic-settings  (MIT)

The above components are listed as dependencies in server/pyproject.toml
and installed at build time. No source code from them is redistributed
in this repository.
